      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-09-24</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-09-20T18:44:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ranked Choice Voting Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires each state to carry out elections for Senators and Representatives in Congress, including primary, special, and general elections, using a system of ranked choice voting. Under this system, each voter must rank the candidates for the office in order of the voter's preference.<br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
